OL,3,CWhy am I struggling to sleep and what
OL,4,Ccan I do?
OL,6,F"We're constantly switched on. There
OL,7,Fis not enough down time," he said.
OL,8,F"That can also have an effect on sleep
OL,9,Fdifficulties."
OL,11,FHe continued: "Plus the expectation of
OL,12,Fwork and jobs, being stressed - all of
OL,13,Fthose combined can have that effect."
OL,15,FWhat can be done about it?
OL,17,FThere are some NHS sleep services in
OL,18,FWales, including the Aneurin Bevan
OL,19,FSleep Centre in Abergavenny and the
OL,20,FGwent Sleep Unit at the Royal Gwent
OL,21,FHospital.
