OL,3,CWhy am I struggling to sleep and what
OL,4,Ccan I do?
OL,6,FHowever, Dr Sakhuja feels there is a
OL,7,Flack of dedicated sleep services and
OL,8,Fclinicians with a specialism in sleep
OL,9,Fdisorders or sleep medicine in Wales.
OL,11,F"The reality is the resources for
OL,12,Fsleep medicine or sleep disorders are
OL,13,Fnot that much prevalent within the
OL,14,FNHS. There are only very few dedicated
OL,15,Fsleep services within the NHS in Wales
OL,16,Fas well as throughout the UK," he said.
