OL,3,CWhy am I struggling to sleep and what
OL,4,Ccan I do?
OL,6,F"Many people have to wait for a long
OL,7,Ftime to get to see a specialist who
OL,8,Fspecialises or has an interest in
OL,9,Fsleep medicine and they're just
OL,10,Fquietly suffering because of the time
OL,11,Fit takes to see them."
OL,13,FDr Sakhuja had some tips for those
OL,14,Flooking to adjust their lifestyle to
OL,15,Fimprove their sleep. He recommended:
